| `enmity_raw`                  | 0.625 | 0.419     | 0.00  | 0.60  | 0.80  | 0.83  | 0.90  |
| `amity_raw`                   | 0.575 | 0.403     | 0.00  | 0.45  | 0.70  | 0.83  | 0.90  |
